==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Infinitely
<hw>In"fi*nite*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Without bounds
or limits; beyond or below assignable limits; <as>as, an
<ex>infinitely</ex> large or <ex>infinitely</ex> small
quantity</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Very; exceedingly; vastly; highly; extremely.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Infinitely</xex> pleased.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Dryden.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Infiniteness</ent>⟦br⟧
